attributes.text: Turn left, then turn right on St Mary's Rd
Bear right to merge onto Perimeter Hwy (TC-100 W)
Take the exit on the right to merge onto the highway toward MB-3
Make a U-turn at Service Rd and go back on McGillivray Blvd (MB-3)
Take the exit on the right to merge onto Perimeter Hwy (TC-100 W)
Take exit 42A on the right to merge onto City Rte-85 E / Portage Av
At the traffic light, turn left on Sturgeon Rd
Finish at Location 2, on the right
